<span class="displaytext">(candidate full) issued the following statement: <p>"the workers at cbs news have been without a contract for close to two and a half years. it is my hope that both sides will reach an agreement that results in a secure contract for the workers at cbs news but let me be clear: </p><p>"i will honor the picket line if the workers at cbs news decide to strike. </p><p>"america's unions are the backbone of america's middle class and i will always stand with america's working men and women in the fight to ensure that they are able to earn a fair wage."</p></span>



